<refsect2 id="hb-uniscribe-font-get-hfont" role="function">
<title>hb_uniscribe_font_get_hfont&#160;()</title>
<indexterm zone="hb-uniscribe-font-get-hfont"><primary>hb_uniscribe_font_get_hfont</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C"><link linkend="HFONT:CAPS"><returnvalue>HFONT</returnvalue></link>
hb_uniscribe_font_get_hfont (<parameter><link linkend="hb-font-t"><type>hb_font_t</type></link> *font</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>Fetches the HFONT handle that corresponds to the
specified <link linkend="hb-font-t"><type>hb_font_t</type></link> font.</para>
